name: RareLinkImplementationGuide
title: RareLink Implementation Guide
description: An Implementation Guide for RareLink Common Data Model, based on the ontology-based rare disease common data model (RD-CDM) harmonising the European Rare Disease Infrastructure Common Data Set, HL7 FHIR R4, and Phenopackets; and integrating the IPS 2.0.0 profiles and Genomics Reporting 3.0.0 profiles.
